{
  "stem": "5255.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because many of the people that were marching fell dead on the road.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we had to bury them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So he was asking for volunteers to dig graves to bury the people that fell dead.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So I was a volunteer to go to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the reason I was volunteering is I thought that maybe I'm going to meet a civilian.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But every time I meet a civilian, I somehow talk him into bringing me some food.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But as luck had it, I didn't have  a chance to meet any civilians right away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But that was April the 21st, 1945.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I was digging graves in Bavaria on the side of a road.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And there were-- I had four other people, Hungarian Jews that didn't speak Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I had a hard time conversing with them, but somehow we made it happen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we were digging graves together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We used to put in six to eight people in a grave.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And on the night of the 22nd, following night, about 12 o'clock at night, it was raining so strongly that I asked the guard who was guarding us that we cannot work any longer.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I told him, we have to go into a farm to dry out and get something to eat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Otherwise, we're going to have to be put into these graves ourselves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And he-- he agreed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But he told me, but you have to knock on the door and you have to answer the question.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I says, I will.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And he saw that I have-- you know, I have a spade in my hand, a shovel.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And it was raining, so he has his [? carabine ?] turned around.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And he was covered up with a raincoat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "So he couldn't move.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
